0:
”Alexa, ask Carolina Panthers Records, who has the single season record for passing yards?”
”Who has the most rushing touchdowns in Panthers history?”
”Who is the Carolina Panthers all-time leader in sacks?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: carolina panthers records
des: This skill provides statistical records for the Carolina Panthers NFL football team. This is an unofficial skill, not endorsed by the Carolina Panthers. Ask for Carolina Panthers record-holders in stats like passing, rushing, receiving, sacks, and interceptions. This skill covers both single-season and all-time records.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
